Use the actual vendor list from `compliance/vendors.md`. Generate 5-7 phishing scenarios that look real to Hall's team:

```
SCENARIO 1 — Vendor SSO password expiry
═══════════════════════════════════════
Real sender field:     security@auth-okta-support.com
Spoofed brand:         Okta (you actually use Okta)
Pretext:               "Your Okta password expires in 24 hours. Click to extend."
Tell:                  Domain is auth-okta-support.com, not okta.com.
