SCENARIO 2 — Stripe payout failed
═════════════════════════════════
Real sender field:     payouts-team@stripe-payments-help.com
Spoofed brand:         Stripe
Pretext:               "Your $4,283 payout failed. Update bank info to retry."
Tell:                  Real Stripe sends from no-reply@stripe.com or related@stripe.com.
