### Phase 3 — Quiz generation

Generate 10 multiple-choice questions per topic. The quiz is the audit artifact.

```
QUIZ — Phishing Awareness (annual)
═══════════════════════════════════

Q1: You receive an email from "billing@stripe-support.com" saying your
    payout failed. What's the right action?
    A) Click the link — it's faster
    B) Forward to security@ours.com and ignore the email
    C) Open dashboard.stripe.com directly; check there
    D) Reply asking for proof

Answer: C. Real Stripe issues surface in the dashboard. Don't trust email links
       for financial info.

Q2: ...
```

10 questions, mix of:
- 3 vendor-specific phishing scenarios
- 2 secure-coding pattern recognition (here's a snippet; spot the vuln)
- 2 data-handling rule application (you have X data, can you put it in Y?)
- 2 IR procedure recall (what's the SEV-1 threshold?)
- 1 threat-model awareness (what's our biggest STRIDE risk?)

Pass threshold: 8/10. Required for compliance evidence.

